    ConsumerFactoryFeature<T>
    Binds Feature to ConsumerFactory to indicate that the value consumer factory must be executed in order to obtain a consumer (builder) to which the object being configured should be passed.
    interface 
    SupplierFactoryFeature<T>
    Binds Feature to SupplierFactory to indicate that the value supplier factory must be executed in order to obtain the final feature value.
